This is an interactive Mandelbrot fractal viewer written in Python 3.
To run it, install Python 3 [1] and PyQt4 [2] and start main.py.

Demo control:
Esc, Ctrl-Q			Exit
Arrow keys			Pan camera
+/=				Zoom in camera
-/_				Zoom out camera
Left mouse button		Pan camera
Middle mouse button		Zoom in/out camera

Homepage: http://github.com/skaslev/pyman/
Author: Slavomir Kaslev <slavomir.kaslev@gmail.com>

[1] http://python.org/download/
[2] http://www.riverbankcomputing.co.uk/software/pyqt/download/
